      "comment": "STORM SISTER (1) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Finished in the minors latest when second (19.63) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Solid record here winning four races. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Key chance in this line up. FENCER MAX (5) steps out for the first time at this course. Comes here a last start placegetter at Murray Bridge in a Grade 5 (30.80). Solid formlines coming through his last run. Expected to be in this for a long way. CREEPER (3) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (23.28) at Gawler in a Grade 6. Can improve sharply here. HERE COMES SHAKA (7) can run a bold race on best form.",
